For below programs collect input from user, pi is constant value 3.14 (print output in formatted way)

1.write a program to calculate perimeter of the circle with radius 10.2

## output ##
radius=10.2
perimeter=2*3.14*10.2
print(perimeter)
64.056
print("the perimeter of circule is:" ,perimeter)
the perimeter of circule is: 64.056
print("the perimeter of circule is:{0}" .format(perimeter))
the perimeter of circule is:64.056





2.write a program to calculate area of circle with radius (float) (collect using input function)

## output ##
radius=float(input("enter the radius of circule:"))
enter the radius of circule:40.56
perimeter=2*3.14*40.56
print(perimeter)
254.71680000000003
print("the perimeter of circule is: " perimeter)
SyntaxError: invalid syntax. Perhaps you forgot a comma?
print("the perimeter of circule is: " ,perimeter)
the perimeter of circule is:  254.71680000000003
print("the perimeter of circule is:{0}".format(perimeter))
the perimeter of circule is:254.71


