4.Collect radius and height from user,
calculate Area of cone (area of cone = 0.33 * pi * r * r * h) (int)

## output ##
radius=float(input("enter the radius of cone:"))
enter the radius of cone:23.67
height=float(input("enter the height of cone:"))
enter the height of cone:45.60
area=0.33*23.67*23.67*45.60
print(area)
8430.9264072
print("the area of cone is:{0}".format(area))
the area of cone is:8430.9264072
print("the area of cone is: " ,area)
the area of cone is:  8430.9264072
